import React from "react";
import { Header, Image, Table, Button } from "semantic-ui-react";

const Tablee = props => (
    
  <>
   
    <Table.Body>
      <Table.Row>
        <Table.Cell>
          <Header as="h4" image>
            {props.userType == false ? (
              <Header.Content>
                {props.boke.user[1].first_name +
                  " " +
                  props.boke.user[1].last_name}
              </Header.Content>
            ) : (
              <Header.Content>
                {props.boke.user[0].first_name +
                  " " +
                  props.boke.user[0].last_name}
              </Header.Content>
            )}
          </Header>
        </Table.Cell>
        <Table.Cell>{props.boke.booking_time.split("T")[0]}</Table.Cell>
        <Table.Cell>
          {"0" +
            Math.abs(props.boke.booking_time.split("T")[1].split(":")[0] - 12) +
            ":" +
            props.boke.booking_time.split("T")[1].split(":")[0]}
        </Table.Cell>

        <Table.Cell>{props.boke.booking_status}</Table.Cell>
        {props.userType && (
          <Table.Cell>
            <Button
              inverted
              color="red"
              onClick={props.changeStatus('')}
            >
              Rejection
            </Button>
            <Button
              onClick={props.changeStatus()}
              inverted
              color="green"
            >
              Accept
            </Button>
          </Table.Cell>
        )}
      </Table.Row>
    </Table.Body>
  </>
);
export default Tablee;
